alert.note: Alert for Santa Ynez Mountains Eastern Range; Santa Ynez Mountains Western Range (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Warning issued November 19 at 7:54PM PST until November 19 at 11:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 PM PST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...North winds 30 to 45 mph with gusts to 60 to 70 mph expected. * WHERE...Santa Ynez Mountains Western Range and Santa Ynez Mountains Eastern Range. * WHEN...Until 11 PM PST this evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds will blow down large objects such as trees and power lines. Power outages are likely. Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around large trees. If possible, remain in your home and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.
